Perfect! I found all the CSS classes you're looking for. They are defined in two files. Here's the complete information:

## File Locations and CSS Rules

### File 1: `/client/src/components/HomePage/postCards/postcards.css`

This file contains the primary definitions for the search-related CSS classes:

**`.search-shell`** (lines 11-18)
```css
.search-shell{
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 14;
    align-self: stretch;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
}
```

**`.search-top-bar`** (lines 19-30)
```css
