    position: relative;
    z-index: 12;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.65rem 0.75rem 0.75rem 0.75rem;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-card);
}
```

**`.search-input-wrap`** (lines 31-36)
```css
.search-input-wrap{
    position: relative;
